## 🗃️ Example BigQuery SQL
**HCC candidate extraction (illustrative):**
```sql
SELECT
  c.member_id,
  c.diagnosis_code,
  ANY_VALUE(m.dob) AS member_dob,
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM c.service_date) AS service_year
FROM `project.dataset.claims` AS c
JOIN `project.dataset.members` AS m
  ON m.member_id = c.member_id
WHERE service_date BETWEEN DATE('2025-01-01') AND DATE('2025-12-31')
  AND diagnosis_code IS NOT NULL;
